Asset explore
-------------
You can borrow items from a foreigner (assets (accomodation/car/suplies) with public or friends visibility)
Assets can be filtered by capacity, availability, topic (very similar screen then the event explore)
Assets can have price tag (we haven't introduced purse for public/friends event also)

Features
--------
1) pull up feature if you ended up bottom of the scrolling area (smart list - user retriggers load for next page - it might get back nothing - so the progress circle appears and disappears in this case in an animated way)
2) extract the templates and behaviour (scss/ts/html) to self contained components from activities-popup.component.ts (it's too big) and put under a templates folder next to it (we have three templates here - rate/event/chat)
3) optional events can be parallel with other optional events (does not need to cut optional events), but needs to cut the mandatory events as it is today

Speed
-----
4) curl rating/scrolling animation speed up in most of the places
5) demo creation has got some noticeable slowness on mobile

6) instagram account should be renamed from myscoutee1 to myscoutee, after the other account deleted (deletion period ended apr 3)

7) put a contacts button to show assign members popup without basket
8) on profile editor the school/workspace item can be loaded from a cv (pdf/docx parse)